[[!meta title="Reading and writing emails with Icedove"]]

For reading and writing email, Tails includes <span
class="application">[Icedove](https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/thunderbird/)</span>.

To start <span class="application">Icedove</span> choose
<span class="menuchoice">
  <span class="guimenu">Applications</span>&nbsp;▸
  <span class="guisubmenu">Internet</span>&nbsp;▸
  <span class="guimenuitem">Icedove</span></span>.
